snippet.title: Dead Cells: Everyone is Here! Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Dead Cells' 26th update is here, bringing weapons, skills & skins from Hollow Knight, Blasphemous, Hyper Light Drifter, Guacamelee, Skul & Curse of the Dead Gods!

Available to download now on PC, coming very soon to consoles & Mac.
